OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FVictims of prolific sex offender Alan
OL,8,FHarris, a former solicitor from
OL,9,FPlymouth, have described in harrowing
OL,10,Fdetail the lifelong devastation caused
OL,11,Fby his abuse, as they confronted him
OL,12,Fin court and laid bare the
OL,13,Fpsychological scars they continue to
OL,14,Fendure.
OL,16,FAt Winchester Crown Court, several men
OL,17,Fstood in the witness box and read
OL,18,Ftheir own victim impact statements.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
