FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FMany wept openly as they faced their
OL,8,Fabuser in the dock. Their accounts
OL,9,Fpainted a grim picture of shattered
OL,10,Fchildhoods, addiction, imprisonment
OL,11,Fand enduring shame.
OL,13,FSome of the victims were just children
OL,14,Fwhen the abuse occurred. The court
OL,15,Fheard that offences took place at
OL,16,FCharles Cross Police Station, at a
OL,17,Fmagistrates' court, and even inside
OL,18,Fvictims' own homes.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FOne man told the court that both he
OL,8,Fand his brother had been abused. His
OL,9,Fbrother later died from a heroin
OL,10,Foverdose in 2022. Their mother said
OL,11,Fthe trauma inflicted on her sons drove
OL,12,Fthem towards hard drugs in an attempt
OL,13,Fto numb the shame.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
