FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FSeveral victims described being
OL,8,Fhaunted by Harris's face, plagued by
OL,9,Fflashbacks and nightmares. One man
OL,10,Fsaid he felt as though the abuse was
OL,11,F"written on my face", explaining that
OL,12,Fhe avoids going out because of
OL,13,Foverwhelming feelings of exposure and
OL,14,Fhumiliation.
OL,16,F"I need to put it back in a box," he
OL,17,Ftold the court. "Otherwise I won't
OL,18,Freach 60. I'll go back to drugs and
OL,19,Fprison. I have to put it back into the
OL,20,Fbox."
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]sD@AOUsD@TO]xD@AOUxD@aO]yD@
OL,26,AQOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
