OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FAnother victim revealed that the
OL,8,Fstrain of giving evidence during the
OL,9,Ftrial had been so intense that he
OL,10,Frelapsed into heroin use.
OL,12,FThe court was told that abuse of trust
OL,13,Fwas an overriding factor in this case.
OL,14,FAll the victims were particularly
OL,15,Fvulnerable.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
