FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FSome were very young, others had
OL,8,Fmental health issues, were alcohol
OL,9,Fdependant, drug dependant or both.
OL,10,FMany were isolated - they had no
OL,11,Fchoice but to be there in custody and
OL,12,Fcame in many cases from very unstable
OL,13,Fbackgrounds.
OL,15,FOne man said Harris had preyed upon
OL,16,Fhim at his weakest, when he was
OL,17,Ffrightened, desperate and still a
OL,18,Fchild. He spoke of spending years in
OL,19,Fprison over the past two decades and
OL,20,Fmissing precious time with his
OL,21,Fdaughter.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
