CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,F"My life is a mess," he said. "I have
OL,8,Fterrible insecurities and feelings of
OL,9,Fsuch worthlessness, not a lot of
OL,10,Fconfidence."
OL,12,FIn one of the most emotional moments,
OL,13,Fa victim looked directly at Harris and
OL,14,Fdescribed recurring nightmares about
OL,15,Fhis "evil grin". He said he feels
OL,16,Funclean, bathing three times a day in
OL,17,Fan attempt to rid himself of the
OL,18,F'sense of dirtiness'.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]oD@AOUoD@TO]oD@_OUrD@LO]wD@
OL,26,AEOUwD@OO]
