PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FAnother man told the court he had been
OL,8,Fabused by Harris since childhood,
OL,9,Fincluding during a time when he had
OL,10,Fjust been arrested for murder. He said
OL,11,FHarris had deliberately groomed him,
OL,12,Faware that he had previously been
OL,13,Fexploited by notorious paedophiles
OL,14,FWilliam Goad and Peter Norsworthy.
OL,16,FSeveral victims said they had been
OL,17,Fterrified to come forward, worried
OL,18,Ftheir accounts would be dismissed or
OL,19,Fminimised.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
