PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FHarris, a former Plymouth criminal
OL,8,Fdefence solicitor was found guilty of
OL,9,F10 offences against seven victims, six
OL,10,Fmale and one female, following a five-
OL,11,Fweek trial at Winchester Crown Court.
OL,13,FHarris, of Thorn Park, Plymouth,
OL,14,Fdenied the charges but was found
OL,15,Fguilty of five counts of indecent
OL,16,Fassault and five sexual assaults.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
