PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771945433
OL,3,C"Haunted by his evil grin": Victims
OL,4,Ctell of trauma after abuse by former
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FThe hearing to determine his sentence
OL,8,Fwas told that abuse of trust was an
OL,9,Foverriding factor in this case. All
OL,10,Fthe victims were particularly
OL,11,Fvulnerable.
OL,13,FSome were very young, others had
OL,14,Fmental health issues, were alcohol
OL,15,Fdependant, drug dependant or both.
OL,16,FMany were isolated, they had no choice
OL,17,Fbut to be there in custody and came in
OL,18,Fmany cases from very unstable
OL,19,Fbackgrounds.
OL,21,FThe hearing continues.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@ZO]
